{"link":"https://www.surfspot.nl/customer/account/login/?idp=onegini","html":"<head>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"robots\" content=\"noindex, nofollow\">\n    <meta content=\"ie=edge,chrome=1\" http-equiv=\"x-ua-compatible\">\n    <meta content=\"initial-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no,maximum-scale=1,width=device-width\" name=\"viewport\">\n    <meta content=\"translucent-black\" name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style\">\n    <link href=\"/favicon.ico\" rel=\"shortcut icon\">\n    <!--[if lte IE 8]>\n    <script src=\"/javascripts/html5shiv.min.js\"></script><![endif]-->\n    <link href=\"/stylesheets/application.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <title>SURFconext - POST Data</title>\n</head>\n<body class=\"index\" onload=\"document.forms[0].submit()\">\n<div class=\"mod-redirect\">\n    <img class=\"rotate-img\" src=\"/images/spinner.svg\" alt=\"\">\n\n    <h1>Connecting to the service</h1>\n\n    <p>Waiting for a response from the service.</p>\n\n    <p>Please be patient, it may take a while...</p>\n    <noscript>\n        &lt;p&gt;\n            &lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt;\n            Since your browser does not support JavaScript, you must press the button below to proceed.        &lt;/p&gt;\n    </noscript>\n    <form id=\"ProcessForm\" method=\"post\" action=\"https://www.onegini.me/saml/single-sign-on\">\n        <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"SAMLRequest\" value=\"\">\n\n        \n        <noscript>&lt;input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\" class=\"c-button\" /&gt;</noscript>\n\n        \n    </form>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</body>"}
